Modal App name: warm-pool-server
Custom image: modal.Image.debian_slim()
Class WarmServer with @app.cls(image=image, keep_warm=1)
@modal.enter() setup: initializes self.data_store = {} and self.request_count = 0
@modal.method() handle_request(key, value): stores in self.data_store, increments self.request_count, returns dict
@modal.method() get_stats(): returns {'total_requests': self.request_count, 'stored_keys': list(self.data_store.keys())}
Local entrypoint main() creates WarmServer, calls handle_request.remote twice, calls get_stats.remote(), writes to /home/user/modal_project/server_stats.json
server_stats.json must have total_requests >= 2 and stored_keys containing 'name' and 'role'
Deploy: modal deploy /home/user/modal_project/app.py --env modal-vsdatagen
Run: modal run /home/user/modal_project/app.py --env modal-vsdatagen
App 'warm-pool-server' in modal app list --env modal-vsdatagen
